1
00:00:14,598 --> 00:00:16,517
U prethodnoj epizodi Kuće Davidove...

2
00:00:16,600 --> 00:00:20,896
Ovo je doba kraljeva. Mi smo prva dinastija Izraela.

3
00:00:20,979 --> 00:00:23,858
Oče, zašto me držiš u brdima? Zašto me ne pošalješ u kraljevu vojsku?

4
00:00:23,941 --> 00:00:25,359
Davide, ti si pastir.

5
00:00:25,442 --> 00:00:27,778

    Nisi čovjek od krvi.

    Ja jesam ratnik.

6
00:00:28,362 --> 00:00:30,280
Samuele, večeras slavimo.

7
00:00:30,364 --> 00:00:34,368
Izokrenuo si prijestolje Izraela za vlastitu slavu,

8
00:00:34,451 --> 00:00:39,206
pa ćeš biti predan izopačenoj sili i vlastitoj muci.

9
00:00:39,289 --> 00:00:41,124
Samuele!

10
00:00:41,625 --> 00:00:44,378

    Kamo sada idemo?

    Pronaći kralja.

11
00:00:46,463 --> 00:00:49,633
Neka ga prate. Dovedite mi onoga koga pomazuje.

12
00:00:50,217 --> 00:00:53,595
Davide, Gospodin nad vojskama te je izabrao.

13
00:00:53,679 --> 00:00:56,515

    Za što?

    Za kralja Izraela.

14
00:00:56,598 --> 00:00:59,935
Mora biti ubijen zajedno sa svima u svom domu.

15
00:01:00,018 --> 00:01:02,312

    Što je ovo?

    To je poziv.

16
00:01:02,396 --> 00:01:03,522
Za Davida je.

17
00:01:04,273 --> 00:01:05,774
Moja kraljice, zašto je on ovdje?

18
00:01:05,858 --> 00:01:07,609
Željna sam te čuti kako sviraš.

19
00:01:07,693 --> 00:01:08,986
Drago mi je što si ovdje.

20
00:01:09,069 --> 00:01:11,113
Mikala je kći kraljeva.

21
00:01:11,196 --> 00:01:13,491
Ako postanem dio obitelji, neće biti krvoprolića.

22
00:01:13,574 --> 00:01:15,993
Kraljevi štite krvne loze i uklanjaju prijetnje.

23
00:01:16,076 --> 00:01:18,078
Svi su naši životi ovdje u pitanju.

24
00:01:18,161 --> 00:01:22,040
Kralj se gubi. Svakim ga danom sve manje prepoznajem.

25
00:01:22,124 --> 00:01:24,001
Samuele!

26
00:01:24,084 --> 00:01:26,628
Postoje oni koji još uvijek štuju druge bogove.

27
00:01:26,712 --> 00:01:27,921
Trebam tvoju pomoć.

28
00:01:28,005 --> 00:01:30,007
Pozdravi iz kuće Šaulove.

29
00:01:30,090 --> 00:01:31,175
Golijat!

30
00:01:34,261 --> 00:01:36,722
Dopusti mi da se borim s njihovim kraljem.

31
00:01:37,347 --> 00:01:38,932
Filistejci su se okupili.

32
00:01:39,016 --> 00:01:41,059
Prekrivaju planinu poput pijeska na obali.

33
00:01:41,143 --> 00:01:42,769

    I imaju diva.

    Što?

34
00:01:42,853 --> 00:01:44,229
Gdje je vaš kralj?

35
00:01:44,313 --> 00:01:46,064

    On je samo čovjek, oče.

    Je li?

36
00:01:48,859 --> 00:01:49,860
Oče!

37
00:01:49,943 --> 00:01:52,404
Kako znamo da ovo nije samo slijepa osveta?

38
00:01:52,487 --> 00:01:54,990
Šaul je ubio tvog oca na bojnom polju.

39
00:01:55,073 --> 00:01:56,325
Moramo nešto poduzeti.

40
00:01:56,408 --> 00:01:58,577

    Znaš li kojim putem je Elah?

    Pronaći ću ga.

41
00:01:58,660 --> 00:02:02,164
Natovario sam magarca zalihama. Trebam da ih odneseš.

42
00:02:02,247 --> 00:02:04,124

    Kamo?

    Na bojište.

43
00:02:04,208 --> 00:02:06,960
Tko je ovaj div da prkosi vojskama živoga Boga?

44
00:02:08,545 --> 00:02:11,381
Moramo osigurati da naše prijestolje preživi.

45
00:02:11,465 --> 00:02:12,841
Moraš me okruniti za kralja.

46
00:02:12,925 --> 00:02:14,760
Je li prorok Samuel posjetio vašu obitelj?

47
00:02:14,843 --> 00:02:15,969
Da.

48
00:02:16,053 --> 00:02:18,805
Ako se nitko od vas neće boriti s ovim divom, ja hoću.

49
00:02:18,889 --> 00:02:22,809
Bori se s njim istim duhom koji unosiš u ovu sobu.

50
00:03:01,139 --> 00:03:04,226
Kažu da nije bilo drugog poput njega.

51
00:03:05,811 --> 00:03:08,230
Golijatov mač.

52
00:03:18,240 --> 00:03:23,412
Rođen u vatri, ima snagu bez premca...

53
00:03:25,914 --> 00:03:27,791
za one koji je mogu zauzdati.

54
00:03:27,875 --> 00:03:30,002
Borite se sa mnom!

55
00:03:32,212 --> 00:03:34,965
Promijenio bi način na koji se vode ratovi.

56
00:03:40,429 --> 00:03:42,973
Promijenio bi sam svijet.

57
00:03:45,976 --> 00:03:47,477
Napad!

58
00:03:51,064 --> 00:03:54,860
Oni koji bi vladali njegovom moći osvajali bi narode.

59
00:03:57,154 --> 00:03:59,156
Uništavali bi svoje neprijatelje.

60
00:04:00,991 --> 00:04:05,329
Baš kao što su Filistejci nastojali uništiti nas.

61
00:04:06,872 --> 00:04:11,877
Očajnički želeći zauzeti svoje mjesto kao gospodari nadolazećeg novog doba.

62
00:04:14,838 --> 00:04:18,091
Doba željeza.

63
00:04:19,718 --> 00:04:21,220
Tako kažu.

64
00:04:23,055 --> 00:04:24,723
Ali ja znam istinu.

65
00:04:25,390 --> 00:04:32,147
Mač je moćan samo onoliko koliko je moćan onaj tko njime vlada.

66
00:05:01,677 --> 00:05:03,136
Davide!

67
00:05:10,394 --> 00:05:12,437
Moramo doći do Davida! Naprijed!

68
00:05:12,521 --> 00:05:14,606
Koji je put naprijed?

69
00:05:15,566 --> 00:05:16,567
Elijabe!

70
00:05:22,030 --> 00:05:25,033
Daj nam snage i zaštiti nas.

71
00:05:25,534 --> 00:05:28,036
Stražaru, donesi mi konja i oklop!

72
00:05:29,162 --> 00:05:31,164
Hajde!

73
00:06:08,160 --> 00:06:10,078

    Jonatane!

    Zaštitite princa!

74
00:06:12,414 --> 00:06:13,415
Jonatane!

75
00:06:20,881 --> 00:06:22,424
Formirajte perimetar!

76
00:06:22,508 --> 00:06:23,675
Držite dolinu!

77
00:06:30,015 --> 00:06:31,600

    Trebali bismo napredovati.

    Ne!

78
00:06:31,683 --> 00:06:33,101
Držite ovaj položaj!

79
00:06:38,148 --> 00:06:39,942

    Moram pronaći Davida!

    Moj prinče, čekajte!

80
00:06:45,614 --> 00:06:46,782
Daj mi mač.

81
00:06:51,870 --> 00:06:53,914
Ne.

82
00:06:53,997 --> 00:06:58,043

    Šaule, veliki kralju ratniče.

    Ne.

83
00:06:58,126 --> 00:07:01,630
Ja sam izabrani. Stvoren sam za ovo.

84
00:07:01,713 --> 00:07:03,423
Oče.

85
00:07:03,507 --> 00:07:04,591
Oče.

86
00:07:04,675 --> 00:07:06,510
Što to radiš? Nećeš izaći van.

87
00:07:06,593 --> 00:07:07,928
Dobro sam, Biti.

88
00:07:08,011 --> 00:07:09,012
Oče.

89
00:07:09,680 --> 00:07:11,807
Ti si me sam izveo iz tame.

90
00:07:12,808 --> 00:07:16,395
Sada ja moram voditi ovu vojsku.

91
00:07:17,771 --> 00:07:18,772
Ti ostani ovdje.

92
00:07:20,858 --> 00:07:22,317
Pobrini se da stražari budu postavljeni.

93
00:07:23,193 --> 00:07:24,319
Zaštiti ih!

94
00:07:26,113 --> 00:07:28,115
O, Gospode...

95
00:07:31,159 --> 00:07:32,995
daj nam ovu zemlju!

96
00:07:42,588 --> 00:07:45,215
Moram pronaći svog brata.

97
00:07:46,550 --> 00:07:47,968
Natanaele, ostani blizu.

98
00:07:48,051 --> 00:07:49,136
Davide!

99
00:08:01,648 --> 00:08:03,358
Pošalji ljude na onaj greben.

100
00:08:03,442 --> 00:08:06,361

    Ušutkajte proroka i ne mogu pobijediti.

    Pođite sa mnom!

101
00:08:09,156 --> 00:08:11,283
Naprijed! Pokažite svoju vrijednost!

102
00:08:18,332 --> 00:08:19,708
Elijabe!

103
00:08:23,045 --> 00:08:24,213
Davide!

104
00:09:24,022 --> 00:09:26,775
Hvala ti, Adonai, za ovaj dar.

105
00:09:30,445 --> 00:09:32,906
Ono što činim danas...

106
00:09:33,615 --> 00:09:35,075
...činim u tvoje ime.

107
00:09:53,802 --> 00:09:55,637
To je čvrsta bronca.

108
00:09:56,763 --> 00:09:59,016
Najjači metal na Zemlji.

109
00:10:01,143 --> 00:10:05,189
Iskovan od otopljenih oštrica poraženih Filistejaca.

110
00:10:15,699 --> 00:10:16,867
Sviđa li ti se?

111
00:10:18,660 --> 00:10:20,996
Dobro. Jer sam ga dao napraviti za tebe.

112
00:10:22,039 --> 00:10:24,249
To je kraljevski mač, isti kao moj.

113
00:10:25,250 --> 00:10:29,922
Urezan s poviješću našeg naroda i molitvom Bogu.

114
00:10:30,005 --> 00:10:34,009
Koristit ćeš ga s vjerom, da zaštitiš naš narod i poraziš naše neprijatelje.

115
00:10:34,510 --> 00:10:37,638
Jer jednoga dana, bit ćeš veliki ratnik.

116
00:10:39,932 --> 00:10:41,308
Kralju moj, vrijeme je.

117
00:10:43,644 --> 00:10:44,645
Pođi sa mnom.

118
00:10:54,488 --> 00:10:55,656
Maok...

119
00:10:59,201 --> 00:11:00,661
tvoja vladavina je završila.

120
00:11:06,917 --> 00:11:08,293
Narode moj,

121
00:11:09,044 --> 00:11:12,214
Gat više neće mučiti Izrael.

122
00:11:16,552 --> 00:11:21,765
Sagradit ću svoju tvrđavu ondje gdje je nekoć stajala tvoja utvrda.

123
00:11:26,979 --> 00:11:28,021
Oče!

124
00:11:39,825 --> 00:11:41,201
Ne!

125
00:12:00,429 --> 00:12:02,181
Bog je s nama!

126
00:12:54,733 --> 00:12:56,109
Davide!

127
00:13:02,449 --> 00:13:03,450
Jonatane!

128
00:13:03,534 --> 00:13:05,494

    Jesi li dobro?

    Jesam.

129
00:13:05,577 --> 00:13:08,330
Dobro. Ostani blizu. Dolje. Strijele!

130
00:13:10,415 --> 00:13:11,792
Nikad se prije nisi borio u bitci?

131
00:13:11,875 --> 00:13:13,252
Ne prije danas, ne.

132
00:13:16,421 --> 00:13:19,174
Prvo pravilo, ostani miran.

133
00:13:19,258 --> 00:13:22,928
Gledaj gore, a kad napadaš, bodi, ne sijeci.

134
00:13:23,428 --> 00:13:26,390
Sjeti se, Bog je bio s tobom kad si ubio ovog diva.

135
00:13:26,473 --> 00:13:27,891
I još uvijek je... Mici se!

136
00:13:31,812 --> 00:13:33,146

    Ostani blizu...

    U redu.

137
00:13:33,230 --> 00:13:35,270
-...štit gore, pazi na strijele.

    Aha.

138
00:13:35,649 --> 00:13:37,067
Idemo.

139
00:13:49,079 --> 00:13:50,330
Strijele!

140
00:13:57,129 --> 00:13:58,338
Imam ideju.

141
00:14:04,553 --> 00:14:07,222
Bit će pobjednici, zar ne?

142
00:14:07,306 --> 00:14:09,349

    Otac je uvijek pobjednik.

    Da, naravno.

143
00:14:10,392 --> 00:14:12,186
Zašto onda izgledaš zabrinuto?

144
00:14:14,730 --> 00:14:18,233
Mikala, prestani. Činiš me nervoznom.

145
00:14:20,527 --> 00:14:21,570
Meraba, ostani tu.

146
00:14:31,580 --> 00:14:32,623
Što je?

147
00:14:32,706 --> 00:14:34,791
Mislila sam da smo ovdje sigurne.

148
00:14:34,875 --> 00:14:37,211
To je druga vojska. Okruženi smo.

149
00:14:38,045 --> 00:14:39,671
Ubilili su našu stražu.

150
00:14:42,090 --> 00:14:44,092
Meraba, ovo je kraljev šator.

151
00:14:44,176 --> 00:14:46,428
To je prvo mjesto kamo će doći. Moramo se maknuti.

152
00:14:46,512 --> 00:14:47,513
Ne možemo.

153
00:14:47,596 --> 00:14:49,264
Moramo se maknuti sada.

154
00:14:50,182 --> 00:14:51,183
Uzmi nož.

155
00:15:01,527 --> 00:15:02,778
Sada, sada.

156
00:15:15,374 --> 00:15:18,377
Šaule...

157
00:15:21,213 --> 00:15:22,214
Agag?

158
00:15:40,440 --> 00:15:43,443
Šaule...

159
00:16:26,028 --> 00:16:27,362
Ovo je kaos.

160
00:16:27,446 --> 00:16:28,906
Joabe, što je to?

161
00:16:28,989 --> 00:16:30,908
Naprijed! Naprijed!

162
00:16:39,958 --> 00:16:41,335
Prinče moj!

163
00:16:42,419 --> 00:16:43,504
Davide.

164
00:16:43,587 --> 00:16:46,548
Abnere. Makni Davida s polja, a onda napreduj.

165
00:16:47,132 --> 00:16:48,217
Konačno!

166
00:16:48,300 --> 00:16:49,426
Mogu se boriti s tobom.

167
00:16:49,510 --> 00:16:51,303
Ganjat ćemo ih sve do Gata.

168
00:16:51,386 --> 00:16:52,471
Bog je s nama.

169
00:16:52,554 --> 00:16:53,555
Da, moj prinče.

170
00:16:54,473 --> 00:16:55,474
Držite liniju!

171
00:16:55,557 --> 00:16:57,976

    Kamo ideš?

    Idem pronaći oca.

172
00:16:58,060 --> 00:16:59,603

    Idem s tobom...

    Ne!

173
00:16:59,686 --> 00:17:01,981

    Obavio si svoje.

    Pusti me da se borim s tobom, Jonatane.

174
00:17:02,064 --> 00:17:04,608

    Ne danas! Idi!

    Hajde sada.

175
00:17:04,691 --> 00:17:06,401
Jesi li vidio moju braću?

176
00:17:07,069 --> 00:17:09,696
Elijabe! Elijabe!

177
00:17:14,785 --> 00:17:17,454
Natanaele! Ostani blizu.

178
00:17:17,538 --> 00:17:20,332

    Abinadabe! Čekaj! Čekaj! Ne, ne!

    Ostani s nama!

179
00:17:20,415 --> 00:17:22,501
Gdje si? Ne vidim.

180
00:17:22,584 --> 00:17:24,086

    Ustani!

    Čekaj! Ne, čekaj!

181
00:17:26,046 --> 00:17:28,966
Elijabe! Elijabe! Elijabe!

182
00:17:33,637 --> 00:17:35,681
Nikad ne prestaj se boriti, brate. Nikad!

183
00:17:35,764 --> 00:17:38,892
Uzmi mač i idi do Davida. Idi, Natanaele! Idi!

184
00:18:17,890 --> 00:18:20,767
Agag! Vrati se!

185
00:18:27,149 --> 00:18:28,650
Moramo ići. Hajde.

186
00:18:30,152 --> 00:18:31,695
U redu, idemo, idemo.

187
00:18:44,499 --> 00:18:46,168

    Što je?

    Ostani dolje, ostani dolje.

188
00:18:50,214 --> 00:18:51,423
Imaju još divova.

189
00:18:57,846 --> 00:18:59,765
Napadnite dolinu!

190
00:19:08,357 --> 00:19:10,817
Okupi što više plemena možeš.

191
00:19:10,901 --> 00:19:13,779
Reci im da ćemo napredovati na moj znak. Idi!

192
00:19:13,862 --> 00:19:15,447
Napravite mjesta. Napravite mjesta.

193
00:19:15,531 --> 00:19:16,532
Prođite.

194
00:19:17,950 --> 00:19:18,951
Davide!

195
00:19:20,786 --> 00:19:22,079
Elijabe!

196
00:19:22,162 --> 00:19:23,330

    Živ si?

    Jesam.

197
00:19:23,413 --> 00:19:24,540
Hvala Bogu.

198
00:19:24,623 --> 00:19:26,750
Da. I Jonatanu. Dugujem mu život.

199
00:19:27,334 --> 00:19:29,670

    Trebao sam biti s tobom, brate.

    Sada si ovdje.

200
00:19:29,753 --> 00:19:31,004
Elijabe!

201
00:19:38,846 --> 00:19:40,639
Zasjeda!

202
00:19:40,722 --> 00:19:43,308
Držite liniju. Držite. Držite.

203
00:19:46,645 --> 00:19:48,522
To su ljudi kralja Ašdoda.

204
00:19:48,605 --> 00:19:50,232
Žele nas okružiti.

205
00:19:50,315 --> 00:19:53,610
Traži Davida. Ne možemo ih još dugo zadržavati.

206
00:19:53,694 --> 00:19:55,321

    Odvest ću Davida s bojišta.

    Ne!

207
00:19:55,404 --> 00:19:57,281

    Očisti polje!

    Povedi nekoliko ljudi sa sobom.

208
00:19:57,364 --> 00:19:58,532
Abi... Abinadabe! Mogu se boriti!

209
00:20:10,294 --> 00:20:11,378
Eto, eto.

210
00:20:11,461 --> 00:20:12,462
Jesi li spreman?

211
00:20:13,589 --> 00:20:14,715
Mislim da ne mogu.

212
00:20:14,798 --> 00:20:16,175
Nemamo vremena.

213
00:20:17,801 --> 00:20:18,802
Idi.

214
00:20:20,470 --> 00:20:22,514

    Gospodine! Gospodine!

    Pratite ih!

215
00:20:34,193 --> 00:20:37,070

    Elijabe!

    To je on! Ubijte tog dečka!

216
00:20:40,532 --> 00:20:42,784

    Elijabe! Elijabe!

    Trči! Idi!

217
00:20:42,868 --> 00:20:44,203
Idi! Idi!

218
00:20:44,745 --> 00:20:46,163
Ubijte dečka! Idi!

219
00:21:12,814 --> 00:21:14,650
Taj dečko je moj brat!

220
00:21:17,903 --> 00:21:21,532

    Kralj je mrtav! Povlačenje.

    Povucite se. Povlačenje.

221
00:21:21,615 --> 00:21:24,284

    Povlačenje.

    Ne! Ne, ostanite u borbi!

222
00:21:24,368 --> 00:21:25,702
Pošaljite signal!

223
00:21:26,495 --> 00:21:28,956
Potisnut ćemo ih sve do Gata!

224
00:21:38,715 --> 00:21:41,009
Naprijed!

225
00:21:44,471 --> 00:21:48,517
Slijedite me! Za pleme Judino!

226
00:21:52,312 --> 00:21:54,064
Potisnite ih!

227
00:22:05,367 --> 00:22:07,286
Daj nam snage, o, Gospode.

228
00:22:08,579 --> 00:22:10,414
Daj nam ovu zemlju.

229
00:22:11,290 --> 00:22:13,250
Kao u dane Mojsijeve,

230
00:22:13,750 --> 00:22:16,670
štiti nas noću u stupu od ognja!

231
00:22:19,173 --> 00:22:21,049
Podari nam pobjedu.

232
00:22:23,844 --> 00:22:25,971
Daj nam ovu zemlju!

233
00:22:26,054 --> 00:22:27,681
Povucite se!

234
00:22:33,145 --> 00:22:35,856
Šaule...

235
00:22:35,939 --> 00:22:37,357
Ne možeš se sakriti od mene.

236
00:22:37,858 --> 00:22:40,694
Šaule...

237
00:22:46,992 --> 00:22:48,869
Šaule...

238
00:22:52,748 --> 00:22:54,917
Šaule...

239
00:22:59,338 --> 00:30:01,882
Veliki kralju ratniče.

240
00:23:03,550 --> 00:23:08,055
Ali nisi me porazio.

241
00:23:28,116 --> 00:23:29,535

    Sakrij se. Sakrij se!

    U redu.

242
00:23:30,285 --> 00:23:31,286
Sakrij se!

243
00:23:32,079 --> 00:23:33,288
Abinadabe.

244
00:23:33,789 --> 00:23:36,124
Ovo ne pomaže, Davide. Spusti se.

245
00:23:36,208 --> 00:23:38,377

    Ubio sam lava s njim.

    Znamo.

246
00:23:38,460 --> 00:23:40,671
Samo sjedni, za milost Božju.

247
00:23:41,839 --> 00:23:43,090
Sjedni!

248
00:23:46,009 --> 00:23:47,928
Moramo odvesti Davida na sigurno.

249
00:23:48,011 --> 00:23:50,138
Okruženi smo, brate. Nema sigurnosti.

250
00:24:40,105 --> 00:24:42,316
Abinadabe, gdje je David?

251
00:24:43,025 --> 00:24:44,193
Natanaele!

252
00:24:44,276 --> 00:24:45,277
Upravo je bio ovdje.

253
00:24:45,360 --> 00:24:46,778
Onda idi i nađi ga!

254
00:24:50,866 --> 00:24:53,452

    Davide.

    Brate. Izvuci me odavde.

255
00:24:53,535 --> 00:24:54,786
Ustani! Idi.

256
00:25:23,398 --> 00:25:26,109
Oče, zašto se borimo?

257
00:25:26,652 --> 00:25:29,404
Zašto se borimo?

258
00:25:33,116 --> 00:25:36,870
Reci mi, što radi pastir?

259
00:25:38,372 --> 00:25:40,123
On čuva ovce.

260
00:25:40,207 --> 00:25:42,668
Tako je. A znaš li zašto?

261
00:25:45,879 --> 00:25:50,634
Jer na ovom svijetu ima lavova i vukova.

262
00:25:50,717 --> 00:25:55,889
A ako se pastir ne bori s njima kad dođu, njegove ovce će biti pojedene.

263
00:25:56,807 --> 00:25:59,351
I uskoro će njegovo stado nestati.

264
00:25:59,434 --> 00:26:02,104
Više neće biti pastir,

265
00:26:02,729 --> 00:26:07,609
i sve što će ostati su lavovi i vukovi.

266
00:26:09,653 --> 00:26:11,280
Zato se borimo.

267
00:26:12,614 --> 00:26:13,949
Da zaštitimo svoje stado.

268
00:26:14,741 --> 00:26:19,830
Naš narod, naše zemlje i sve što nam je drago.

269
00:26:20,330 --> 00:26:23,667
Da i mi ne bismo nestali.

270
00:26:24,710 --> 00:26:27,004
Ali ja se ne znam boriti.

271
00:26:28,005 --> 00:26:29,882
Onda ću te ja naučiti,

272
00:26:29,965 --> 00:26:35,220
da se jednog dana možeš boriti s lavovima i vukovima.

273
00:26:35,304 --> 00:26:36,680
Mikala!

274
00:27:01,622 --> 00:27:03,832
Meraba, jesi li dobro? Jesi li dobro?

275
00:27:03,916 --> 00:27:06,793

    Krv. Imam krv na sebi.

    Moramo ići. Moramo ići.

276
00:27:18,764 --> 00:27:20,516
Nat! Nastavi se boriti!

277
00:27:26,563 --> 00:27:27,564
Ne!

278
00:27:42,829 --> 00:27:44,748
Ne! Natanaele!

279
00:28:46,977 --> 00:28:48,937
Daj mi snage.

280
00:28:51,023 --> 00:28:55,194
O, Gospode. Pomozi mi da se sjetim boljih dana...

281
00:29:09,499 --> 00:29:14,254
Šaul. Sin Kišev, vođa plemena Benjaminova.

282
00:29:15,756 --> 00:29:18,759
Kralj svega Izraela.

283
00:29:19,551 --> 00:29:22,137
Svevišnji obasjava te svojim svjetlom danas,

284
00:29:23,263 --> 00:29:29,019
kao što je to učinio prije mnogo godina kad je njegov narod zavapio za kraljem da ih ujedini.

285
00:29:29,728 --> 00:29:34,024
Pozvao je tebe, svog vjernog slugu,

286
00:29:34,650 --> 00:29:38,403
da ih vodiš, da ih štitiš,

287
00:29:38,487 --> 00:29:40,405
i ti si to učinio,

288
00:29:40,489 --> 00:29:45,744
ostvarujući velike pobjede u njegovo ime i za njegovu slavu.

289
00:29:46,828 --> 00:29:48,622
Dugo vladao.

290
00:29:49,623 --> 00:29:54,044
Neka tvoja kuća vlada kraljevstvom generacijama koje dolaze.

291
00:29:55,337 --> 00:29:58,382
Šaule, kad si bio malen u vlastitim očima,

292
00:29:58,465 --> 00:30:01,301
Gospodin te je podigao i učinio kraljem.

293
00:30:01,385 --> 00:30:05,180
Sada kad si velik u vlastitim očima,

294
00:30:05,264 --> 00:30:10,310
pobunio si se i učinio se zlim u očima Gospodnjim.

295
00:30:10,811 --> 00:30:13,188
Zlim?

296
00:30:13,772 --> 00:30:17,276
Izokrenuo si prijestolje Izraela za vlastitu slavu,

297
00:30:17,359 --> 00:30:22,072
pa ćeš biti predan izopačenoj sili i vlastitoj muci.

298
00:30:22,155 --> 00:30:24,116
Sam si.

299
00:30:24,199 --> 00:30:26,618
Gospodin je otrgnuo kraljevstvo od tebe.

300
00:30:26,702 --> 00:30:28,328
Napušten.

301
00:30:28,412 --> 00:30:29,872
Sada bira drugoga.

302
00:30:29,955 --> 00:30:31,623
Ostavljen.

303
00:30:31,707 --> 00:30:33,667
Čovjeka po svom srcu.

304
00:30:34,376 --> 00:30:38,839
Kralj bez svoga Boga.

305
00:30:38,922 --> 00:30:40,257
Samuele!

306
00:30:59,318 --> 00:31:00,402
Gotovo je.

307
00:31:05,240 --> 00:31:08,660
Završeno je.

308
00:31:16,001 --> 00:31:17,085
Završeno je!

309
00:31:19,588 --> 00:31:22,591
Ne, nije gotovo.

310
00:31:30,599 --> 00:31:32,518
Propustili ste veći dio bitke, kralju.

311
00:31:33,685 --> 00:31:35,312
Sada bitka dolazi k vama.

312
00:31:36,396 --> 00:31:39,733
Akiš. Sin Maokov.

313
00:31:42,236 --> 00:31:43,820
Činite mi veliku čast.

314
00:31:43,904 --> 00:31:47,074
Častiti vas nije mi namjera.

315
00:31:47,908 --> 00:31:51,787
Ipak, sve ovo, cijela vaša kampanja je zbog mene.

316
00:31:52,371 --> 00:31:54,456
I vaše žeđi da osvetite svog oca.

317
00:31:54,957 --> 00:31:56,542
I da vratim svoj narod

318
00:31:57,292 --> 00:32:00,546
na njihovo pravo mjesto kao vladare nad vašim.

319
00:32:02,464 --> 00:32:05,133
Vaš otac je imao slične ambicije.

320
00:32:05,843 --> 00:32:07,636
Pokazale su se kao njegova propast.

321
00:32:07,719 --> 00:32:10,055
Oh, shvatit ćete da ja nisam svoj otac.

322
00:32:10,138 --> 00:32:12,349
Da, niste.

323
00:33:01,440 --> 00:33:03,317
Kakva je ovo mračna poganska magija?

324
00:33:03,400 --> 00:33:06,570
Nije magija, Šaule. Sudbina.

325
00:33:09,656 --> 00:33:11,200
Ovo je za mog oca.

326
00:34:15,347 --> 00:34:16,849
Rane te izdaju.

327
00:34:22,437 --> 00:34:23,689
Ubojico divova.

328
00:34:27,067 --> 00:34:28,485
Glupi dečko.

329
00:34:50,090 --> 00:34:51,133
Dovrši to.

330
00:34:52,050 --> 00:34:54,303
Ili ću te ja, bogova mi, dovršiti, Jonatane.

331
00:34:54,386 --> 00:34:56,263

    Dovrši to!

    Jonatane!

332
00:35:00,058 --> 00:35:01,143
Jonatane!

333
00:35:08,859 --> 00:35:10,027
Što to radiš?

334
00:35:10,110 --> 00:35:12,988
Dobit ćete svoju osvetu, kralju, ali ne danas.

335
00:35:13,071 --> 00:35:14,489
Ne!

336
00:35:17,451 --> 00:35:19,536
Jonatane. Jonatane.

337
00:35:21,121 --> 00:35:23,707
Ja sam. Ja sam. Ja sam.

338
00:35:24,374 --> 00:35:25,584
Jesi li dobro?

339
00:35:25,667 --> 00:35:28,504
Davide, što je s bitkom?

340
00:35:33,133 --> 00:35:34,426
Bježe.

341
00:35:35,469 --> 00:35:37,596
Ganjamo ih do vrata Gata.

342
00:35:39,223 --> 00:35:40,474
Gotovo je.

343
00:35:46,730 --> 00:35:48,065
Moram ići pronaći svoju braću.

344
00:35:48,649 --> 00:35:52,945
Idi. Idi. Ja ću se pobrinuti za oca, idi.

345
00:35:57,115 --> 00:35:58,158
U redu.

346
00:36:07,459 --> 00:36:08,627
Sine moj.

347
00:36:10,379 --> 00:36:11,380
Dođi.

348
00:36:17,928 --> 00:36:18,929
Gdje je Akiš?

349
00:36:19,847 --> 00:36:20,973
Pobjegao je.

350
00:36:23,725 --> 00:36:24,810
Nema veze.

351
00:36:26,436 --> 00:36:27,813
Bitka je dobivena.

352
00:36:28,647 --> 00:36:29,731
Dobro.

353
00:36:30,732 --> 00:36:33,777
Dobro, sine moj. Dobro.

354
00:36:37,281 --> 00:36:38,365
Nisi ozlijeđen?

355
00:36:38,907 --> 00:36:40,284
Ne, dobro sam.

356
00:36:44,246 --> 00:36:45,455
Idemo.

357
00:37:38,842 --> 00:37:40,719
Pobjeda!

358
00:37:44,473 --> 00:37:46,183
Pobjeda!

359
00:37:57,903 --> 00:37:59,238
Ubojico divova!

360
00:38:09,081 --> 00:38:10,290
Bravo, dečko.

361
00:38:12,751 --> 00:38:13,919
Davide.

362
00:38:14,503 --> 00:38:17,714
Nemoj mi tako nestajati. Ha?

363
00:38:47,661 --> 00:38:48,662
Eli...

364
00:38:48,745 --> 00:38:49,913
Ovdje sam.

365
00:38:49,997 --> 00:38:52,749
Ovdje sam s tobom.

366
00:38:57,087 --> 00:38:58,630

    Diši.

    Eli...

367
00:38:58,714 --> 00:38:59,715
Da?

368
00:39:03,594 --> 00:39:05,762
Možemo li sada ići kući?

369
00:39:06,972 --> 00:39:08,473
Da, Nat.

370
00:39:10,058 --> 00:39:11,727
Da, možemo ići kući.

371
00:39:16,773 --> 00:39:21,361
Reci Davidu da mi je žao što sam sumnjao u njega.

372
00:39:24,156 --> 00:39:25,157
Hoću.

373
00:39:28,744 --> 00:39:29,745
Žao mi je.

374
00:39:36,627 --> 00:39:37,794
N-ne.

375
00:39:56,480 --> 00:39:59,024
Davide! Davide! Davide!

376
00:40:21,171 --> 00:40:22,506
Kćeri moje.

377
00:40:23,882 --> 00:40:25,384
Trebale ste ostati u šatoru.

378
00:40:25,467 --> 00:40:26,760
Logor je bio pregažen.

379
00:40:27,678 --> 00:40:29,054
Kako ste preživjele?

380
00:40:30,848 --> 00:40:31,849
Držale smo se zajedno.

381
00:40:32,599 --> 00:40:33,684
Borile smo se s vukovima.

382
00:40:36,395 --> 00:40:38,313
Moje kćeri su ratnice.

383
00:40:41,149 --> 00:40:42,317
Kralju moj.

384
00:40:46,697 --> 00:40:48,115
Prvače moj!

385
00:40:54,746 --> 00:40:56,874
Znaš, mnogi su sumnjali u tebe.

386
00:40:56,957 --> 00:40:57,958
I sumnjali u mene.

387
00:40:58,834 --> 00:41:00,460
Neki u ovom istom šatoru.

388
00:41:01,253 --> 00:41:03,380
Ali ja sam mogao vidjeti ono što nitko od njih nije mogao.

389
00:41:03,463 --> 00:41:08,552
Božja ruka je na tebi kao što je i na meni.

390
00:41:09,845 --> 00:41:14,308
Ipak, kako to da dječak, glazbenik,

391
00:41:15,142 --> 00:41:19,563
dođe boriti se u mojoj vojsci, ubiti diva,

392
00:41:20,647 --> 00:41:22,191
i spasi mi život?

393
00:41:25,944 --> 00:41:29,031
Reci mi. Tko si ti?

394
00:41:30,908 --> 00:41:32,242
Znate tko sam, kralju moj.

395
00:41:33,368 --> 00:41:34,369
Znam li?

396
00:41:37,956 --> 00:41:39,208
Odakle si došao?

397
00:41:41,126 --> 00:41:43,712
Ja sam pastir iz Judeje. Ništa više.

398
00:41:44,463 --> 00:41:45,589
Pa, pastiru.

399
00:41:45,672 --> 00:41:47,799
Je li prorok Samuel posjetio vašu obitelj?

400
00:41:50,010 --> 00:41:51,011
Da.

401
00:41:52,054 --> 00:41:54,640
Čini se da si sada mnogo više.

402
00:41:55,140 --> 00:41:56,141
Jonatane.

403
00:42:01,021 --> 00:42:04,233
U ime cijelog Izraela, zahvaljujemo ti, Davide.

404
00:42:07,528 --> 00:42:08,695
Sve si nas spasio.

405
00:42:10,948 --> 00:42:15,160
Oče, nema nikoga u cijelom Izraelu dostojnijeg da ga častimo.

406
00:42:20,415 --> 00:42:21,416
Moj mač.

407
00:42:22,668 --> 00:42:23,669
Sada je tvoj.

408
00:42:27,005 --> 00:42:28,131
Hvala vam.

409
00:42:30,259 --> 00:42:34,930
Od danas pa nadalje, dio si kuće Šaulove.

410
00:42:44,731 --> 00:42:45,732
Mikala.

411
00:42:47,401 --> 00:42:48,861
Davide, ti si...

412
00:42:50,612 --> 00:42:52,072
Vratio si mi se.

413
00:42:52,155 --> 00:42:55,075
Uz Božju pomoć, da.

414
00:43:14,428 --> 00:43:15,512
Jesi li dobro?

415
00:43:15,596 --> 00:43:16,597
Da.

416
00:43:18,140 --> 00:43:20,601
Ah, dobro nosiš boje kuće moje obitelji.

417
00:43:20,684 --> 00:43:22,227
Nadam se da ću im biti dorastao.

418
00:43:25,731 --> 00:43:26,982
Ono što si ovdje učinio...

419
00:43:29,359 --> 00:43:31,111
nikada neće biti zaboravljeno.

420
00:43:31,987 --> 00:43:33,739
Ni od strane Izraela, ni od mene.

421
00:43:40,787 --> 00:43:41,830
Jonatane...

422
00:43:43,874 --> 00:43:47,002
postoji li nešto što bi me htio pitati o Samuelu?

423
00:43:51,798 --> 00:43:53,300
Ti si dio moje kuće.

424
00:43:55,093 --> 00:43:56,637
Sada smo braća.

425
00:44:39,346 --> 00:44:40,639
Zanimljivo.

426
00:44:41,265 --> 00:44:43,100
Pssst.

427
00:44:43,183 --> 00:44:45,018

    Dođi ovamo. Dođi.

    Što je, Doeže?

428
00:44:55,028 --> 00:44:59,658
Dostavi ovo Abneru. Samo Abneru.

429
00:45:00,242 --> 00:45:01,410
I ne reci nikome.

430
00:45:14,882 --> 00:45:15,883
Samuele!

431
00:45:39,156 --> 00:45:41,116
Nisam te očekivao ovdje.

432
00:45:46,163 --> 00:45:48,207
Čuo sam da si napustio ove zemlje.

433
00:45:48,957 --> 00:45:51,251
Bio sam protjeran iz ovih zemalja.

434
00:45:53,921 --> 00:45:55,005
Ono što je između nas.

435
00:45:56,006 --> 00:45:58,884

    Ovaj nesporazum je gotov.

    Je li?

436
00:46:00,385 --> 00:46:03,972
Vaš nesporazum nije sa mnom.

437
00:46:04,556 --> 00:46:08,018
Moja muka je prošla. Tama je nestala.

438
00:46:08,101 --> 00:46:11,813
Tvoja muka je tvoje vlastito djelo, Šaule.

439
00:46:12,397 --> 00:46:14,483
Nisi bio napušten od Svevišnjeg.

440
00:46:14,566 --> 00:46:19,947
Ti si bio taj koji ga je napustio i njegovu riječ, u potrazi za vlastitom slavom.

441
00:46:21,990 --> 00:46:25,202
Zašto bi vjerovao da ti je udijelio milost?

442
00:46:25,953 --> 00:46:29,414
Pobijedio sam u ovoj bitci bez tebe.

443
00:46:33,335 --> 00:46:34,336
Bog mi je bio naklonjen.

444
00:46:34,920 --> 00:46:37,548
Uvijek je bio. I dalje jest.

445
00:46:37,631 --> 00:46:39,550
A sada imam novog prvaka.

446
00:46:41,218 --> 00:46:42,678
Ubojicu divova.

447
00:46:44,388 --> 00:46:48,475
Kojeg sam ja izabrao. Sve bez tebe, Samuele.

448
00:46:53,689 --> 00:46:56,191
Dakle, veliki Vidovnjače,

449
00:46:57,776 --> 00:46:59,945
Nudim ti ovaj trenutak.

450
00:47:01,488 --> 00:47:05,993
Ponovno ćeš me pomazati, na ovom svetom tlu, da svi vide.

451
00:47:06,994 --> 00:47:09,079
To ne mogu učiniti.

452
00:47:10,747 --> 00:47:11,748
Zašto ne?

453
00:47:11,832 --> 00:47:13,667
Gospodin to nije zapovjedio.

454
00:47:13,750 --> 00:47:15,127
Kralj je to zapovjedio.

455
00:47:15,210 --> 00:47:21,008
Sigurno do sada znate da ja ne služim kraljevima.

456
00:47:28,599 --> 00:47:29,600
Vrlo dobro.

457
00:47:35,606 --> 00:47:36,607
Straža!

458
00:47:39,818 --> 00:47:41,278
Uhitite Vidovnjaka.

459
00:47:41,361 --> 00:47:42,362
Šaule.

460
00:47:49,745 --> 00:47:51,955
S vremenom ćeš poslušati moje riječi.

461
00:47:54,625 --> 00:47:56,126
Ovo je gotovo, Samuele.

462
00:47:58,962 --> 00:47:59,963
Ne, Šaule.

463
00:48:05,844 --> 00:48:07,304
Tek počinje.

464
00:48:13,519 --> 00:48:15,354
Možda postoji drugi način djelovanja?

465
00:48:15,437 --> 00:48:16,772
Odlučio sam!